SymbolKraft

This product includes software developed by the SymbolCraft project
(https://github.com/kingsword09/SymbolCraft).

SymbolKraft is a modified fork of SymbolCraft. Modifications include renaming the
project and publication coordinates to SymbolKraft/com.ebisuzawa, changing the
public Gradle plugin id and DSL/task names, and updating generated Compose
preview imports to AndroidX Preview.
